{"tid":1747313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1124區選宣言","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:36:38.000Z","uid":124894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76380b82418b5e0389e6a59b5f338e56933c6393","tid":1747313,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"六月開始行，已經行咗六個月，由開頭得幾萬人出嚟，直到今日，已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去到全民反抗</span></span>。我哋係唔係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一直都未輸過？</span></span>唔係，中間發生咗無數咁多事件，<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足死嘅死，傷嘅傷，受性暴力嘅更加不計其數</span></span>。行到今日，面前有一次選舉，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四年前我哋輸到甩褲</span></span>。你問我，選舉緊唔緊要？緊要，不過唔係最緊要，要贏，必須要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭為主，選舉為次</span></span>。港共已經唔止一次剝奪人民嘅選舉權同埋被選舉權，選舉發揮嘅影響力已經大不如前。<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將來嘅嘢一日都嫌多</span></span>，而眼前，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對手只有一個，就係建制</span></span>。建制贏咗，資源一分一毫都唔會擺喺抗爭嗰面，相反，只要我哋同路人攞多一蚊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭嗰面就有機會多一蚊</span></span>。聽日區議會我哋並唔係要贏，而係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對家輸，輸到仆街，要佢哋輸士氣、輸民意</span></span>，之後抗爭路可以再計劃，但係聽日，喺手足面前，喺全世界面前，我哋要再<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贏一場屬於自己嘅仗</span></span>。"},{"pid":"6d93a5560d47d652cbb7bf2733393d561a16ed92","tid":1747313,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"b9077ef8ecfa0ad7a39706898a4042d505f8087c","tid":1747313,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d4653b0e99b1a8f850507540bc47d6e2ef4ce1db","tid":1747313,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:20:43.000Z","msg":"8"},